Ever take a Road trip and thought that this is really boring or the kids get restless? Team Geopuff is here to help save the trip. Since we love road trips we thought this would be a good one to start. We created this series along a particular route we enjoy traveling so keep the name in mind and start your journey on the road to riches! Good Luck
Thanks for doing another Team Geopuff Cache
